  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This prospective validation study evaluates the ability of a risk algorithm, which can
      simultaneously predict the risk of death at 7 days and 30 days for patients with acute heart
      failure presenting to the emergency department. The risk algorithms for prediction of 7-day
      (Emergency Heart failure Mortality Risk Grade [EHMRG]) and 30-day mortality (EHMRG30-ST) have
      been previously derived.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
